name: Imaginary Diatom 2
description: Biphoilic Series - Imaginary diatoms. Diatoms are unicellular algae responsible for most of Earth's oxygen production, their ''skeleton'' constitutes most part of the Sahara desert sand, where the global wind currents sweep the silica-rich diatoms into the Amazon Forest flor, re-fertilizing it. Technique: Illustrator Fibonacci vectors and Photoshop. Dimension: 2000x2000. Contact me on social media to get a full-resolution file for printing. @julioglatt 2021
